SetupNostrAsk
/ Register the channel handler for system actor asks
- on channel 'system', 'default', call goal ../HandleNostrAsk
/ Start listening for Nostr messages (runs in background)
- call goal StartNostrListener async

StartNostrListener
/ Listen for messages and store in cache
/ Read npub from config file (not settings - avoids ask loop)
- read file ../nostr.config, write to %config%
- listen for new message from %config.NostrAskTarget%, call goal OnNostrMessage

OnNostrMessage
/ Cache incoming message for the ask handler to retrieve
- cache %content% for 10 minutes, to 'nostrResponse'
